'''Lorrd''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lorrd/Legends|Lorrd]]. The city was named for the planet itself, and the home to that planet's famed [[Lorrd University|university]]. It was the headquarters of the [[Lorrd Security Force]]s, and the [[Lorrd City Spaceport]] was one of the planet's largest.

[[Hart-and-Parn Gorra-Fiolla|Fiolla]], later assistant [[Auditor-General]] of the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]], hailed from the city of Lorrd.

